Established in the year 2005, we ‘Zeel International’ are engaged in manufacturing and trading a quality assured collection of Stainless Steel Strips that are provided in 200, 300 and 400 series.

Quality Assurance: Our quality controllers are well aware of the changing market trends and ensure to maintain optimum quality standards in all our products. They check the raw material used in the production process, finished products as well as procured products on well defined parameters before these are delivered to the clients.

Client Satisfaction: We are client centric, and our sole objective is attaining utmost customer satisfaction with our products.
